  "content:encoded": "\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table\"><table><tbody><tr><td>Reuters <a href=\"https://app.assets.reuters.com/e/er?utm_campaign=Reuters%20Best%20Weekly_NWSLTR_NEW_GLOB_B2B_2201&utm_medium=email&utm_source=Eloqua&utm_content=B2B%20220922%20Final%20NEWS%20GLOB%20REUTERS%20BEST%20AWARE%20NWSLTR%20WEEKLY&s=2124157686&lid=29235&elqTrackId=69AE39C01B7824BB1E1820FC58F7B249&elq=76105f4682124765986ed20da42de594&elqaid=2367&elqat=1\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">exclusively revealed</a> that Citigroup has submitted a comprehensive multiyear plan to the Federal Reserve and the Office of the Comptroller of the Currency outlining steps to fix weaknesses in its risk management and internal controls. Sources said the plan aims to address a 2020 directive from the Fed demanding that the bank correct several &#8220;longstanding deficiencies&#8221; in its internal controls.</td></tr></tbody></table></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table\"><table><tbody><tr><td></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.reutersagency.com/en/reutersbest/article/reuters-reveals-citigroup-submits-multiyear-plan-to-address-fed-concerns/\">Reuters reveals Citigroup submits multiyear plan to address Fed concerns</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.reutersagency.com/en/\">Reuters News Agency</a>.</p>\n"
